data.description: Are you looking to own a distinctive 2700-square-foot gem nestled on a spacious 3.23-acre lot? Priced well BELOW the most recent appraisal value AND seller is offering $5,000 toward buyer financing concessions today! The open kitchen is not only equipped with efficient storage and cabinetry but also comes with all the appliances you need. Living room boasts a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxation. You'll be amazed by the generous second living space, complete with built-in storage. Convenience is key with main-level laundry room. Owner's suite offers a private deck with a picturesque view of the pond. Three additional well-proportioned bedrooms, along with three full baths and a versatile loft area. Step outside, and you'll find yourself surrounded by the beauty of nature, with the swimming pond featuring a sandy area for your enjoyment. The detached garage is a fantastic space for hobbies or additional storage. Newer HVAC systems, roof, and the septic system has been maintained.  Immediate possession!
